                Capital is cautious; it flows only where it feels secure. In the
                energy sector, that security is not found in the ground, but in
                the unwavering commitment to the agreements that govern its
                extraction. A contract honoured is a nation's most credible
                invitation to invest.
              </h4>
              <span class="quote"
